primary_outcome.description:
0 = no mural thickening (maximal vessel wall thickness <2 mm for aorta, <1mm for its branches)
= mural thickening (2-3 mm for aorta, 1-2 mm for its branches);
= strong thickening (>3 mm for aorta, >2mm for its branches)

secondary_outcome.description:
0= no mural enhancement;
slight mural enhancement;
strong mural enhancement and/or perivascular enhancement

0= no mural edema;
slight mural edema;
strong mural edema
